<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Join Paper Mastery as a Consulting Researcher</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #4F46E5;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4F46E5;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6B7280;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>{{ platform_name }}</h1>
        <p>{{ platform_description }}</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello,</p>
        
        <p>
            We're reaching out because <strong>{{ user_name }}</strong> is interested in consulting with you 
            {% if paper_title %}about your paper "<strong>{{ paper_title }}</strong>"{% endif %}.
        </p>
        
        <p>
            {{ platform_name }} connects researchers like you with readers who want to gain deeper 
            insights beyond what they can learn from reading papers alone. As an expert in your field, 
            your knowledge is valuable!
        </p>
        
        <p><strong>Why join {{ platform_name }} as a consulting researcher?</strong></p>
        
        <ul>
            <li>Set your own hourly rate and availability</li>
            <li>Receive 95%+ of session fees</li>
            <li>Connect with interested readers</li>
            <li>Help others understand your research</li>
            <li>Simple scheduling and video conferencing integration</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>
            To create your researcher profile and start accepting consultation requests, 
            click the button below:
        </p>
        
        <p style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{ registration_url }}" class="cta-button">Create Researcher Profile</a>
        </p>
        
        <p>
            This link will expire in 14 days. If you're not interested in joining the platform, 
            you can simply ignore this email.
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; {{ current_year }} {{ platform_name }}. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>
            If you believe you received this email in error, please disregard it. 
            This is not a newsletter or subscription - this email was sent specifically 
            because a user requested to consult with you.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 